<abstract><t>Networks use tunnels for a variety of reasons.  A large variety of tunnel types are defined and the ingress needs to select a type of tunnel which is supported by the egress and itself.  This document defines how to advertise egress tunnel capabilities in OSPF Router Information Link State Advertisement (LSAs).</t></abstract>

